title: Rock Covers. 40th Anniversary Edition
description:
From legendary releases to ultra-rare records, Elvis Presley to Iron Maiden, discover the 750 album covers that made rock history. Fact sheets, insider interviews, and lists from leading collectors of their top 10 records guide us through the indelible markers of musical memory, complete with bonus info on 250 milestone records that became turning points for a band, an artist, or an entire genre.

  • Hardcover
  • Pages: 512
  • Size: 6.1 x 8.5 in.
